title: about
text:
Hello! My name is Cody (he/him). I’m passionate about progress via technology.
Currently a Technical Product Manager at Voltron Data focusing on data interfaces and awesome OSS like Ibis.
Previously a Product Manager at dbt Labs focusing on OSS (Python models) and Cloud (internal platform). Previously a Product Manager at Azure ML (Microsoft) focusing on data, MLOps, and v2 developer experiences.
See my GitHub and/or LinkedIn for more details on my experience.
I care about (in addition to product management, relevant to work stuff):

OSS & scale
beautiful design
elegant engineering
